{"tid":2039046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國都徹廠了 （中國又贏）","createTime":"2020-05-27T23:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T00:27:50.000Z","uid":254383,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b88bd7833967c19d15955ea8cd4acf74480d571a","tid":2039046,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:18:01.000Z","msg":"標緻汽車母公司標緻雪鐵龍集團（PSA Group）宣布，將與法國國家石油公司道達爾集團（Total）聯手投資約20億元（歐羅．下同），折合約170億港元，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">把電池生產從中國遷回法國</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍680億重振汽車業<br />\n<br />\n標緻雪鐵龍表示，這一舉措是公司增加在法國投資計劃的一部分，包括在法國工廠投資逾4億元的電氣化動力總成（electrified powertrains），以及從2022年開始，在法國工廠生產目前在亞洲採購的零部件。<br />\n<br />\n法國總統馬克龍在當地時間26日宣布，法國政府將出資80億元（約680億港元），重振法國汽車業，以緩解新冠肺炎疫情對經濟的衝擊。該重振汽車業方案涵蓋對電動和混合動力汽車的補貼，旨在助力法國2025年時可以每年生產100萬輛環保汽車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2477078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2477078&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5Pj1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=01d77155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2477078</a>"},{"pid":"d5a15abd2ccc212316d9c61758fbb5963f317d8d","tid":2039046,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:42:59.000Z","msg":"或又成嬴家"},{"pid":"07e373a0715a4dc26113d0d641ba2a05d0dc3571","tid":2039046,"uid":350663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:44:01.000Z","msg":"口裏說不 但身體很誠實"},{"pid":"c02b949bda258ed9c188d94f489775bfdbb48b20","tid":2039046,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:49:19.000Z","msg":"其實咁多國家都係貪平先入中国<br />\n目的係想賺盡<br />\n但中国當左全世界冇左佢唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839a39c3ceb65e214bbc99b277bbd142e7d8808c","tid":2039046,"uid":326897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-2